import React from 'react'
import {FooterContainer, FooterAbout, FooterLogoContainer, FooterLogo, UnorderList, List, FooterWidget, FooterContact} from "./footer.styles";
import Logo from "../../assets/img/logo.png"
const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <FooterContainer>
      <FooterAbout>
        <FooterLogoContainer>
          <FooterLogo src={Logo}/>
        </FooterLogoContainer>
        <UnorderList>
          <List>Address: 60-49 Road 11378 New York</List>
          <List>Phone: +65 11.188.888</List>
          <List>Email: hello@colorlib.com</List>
        </UnorderList>
      </FooterAbout>
      <FooterWidget>a</FooterWidget>
      <FooterContact>b</FooterContact>
    </FooterContainer>
  )
}

export default Footer
